{"tid":1550651,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳惠珠 大埔新達廣場保安想出名","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T19:13:32.000Z","uid":41262,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"505fdc881a5fc4367d30554d72c3879598c8b192","tid":1550651,"uid":41262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7a9Q4gT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7a9Q4gT.jpg&h=f0066415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小弟不才 因傷未能與眾義士共同進退 齊上齊落 只能與一眾街坊遙距聲援 感到非常慚愧<br />\n其間新達廣場住宅保安<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳惠珠</span></span>突然公安上身 上前從後偷拍住戶 令到住戶們感到極度不安 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PoouAoU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPoouAoU.png&h=1c7caab1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7Gv4hn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7Gv4hn.png&h=67f37f38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BcCvjQP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBcCvjQP.png&h=9c6df6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CvWzMvW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvWzMvW.png&h=ec9ab8d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c9woEQ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc9woEQ3.png&h=dd753639&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iD7CKhQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiD7CKhQ.png&h=40eabb44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其後街坊們一齊圍堵<span style=\"color: red;\">陳惠珠</span> 其他保安亦趕上嚟將<span style=\"color: red;\">陳惠珠</span>說服並將相片逐一刪除<br />\n但係 冇人知道刪除前 相片有冇send過出去 <br />\n所以為確保香港人嘅安全 請大家避免聘請<span style=\"color: red;\">陳惠珠</span> 然後幫幫手推post"},{"pid":"4ee90ffe1c939bc1e7d8a9fb616175487d44a967","tid":1550651,"uid":41262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed7ec3a65e155154404f7cb24bfe6e0c1a43b90","tid":1550651,"uid":41262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:59:59.000Z","msg":"妹仔大過主人婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926efe10ab69786b4b973820505719096a1f5d60","tid":1550651,"uid":28970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTRzMBk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTRzMBk.gif&h=5dd35428&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51b90d57140fb06a57b5164f6b9bfeacafdad3b3","tid":1550651,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01cb94381a9d888532d6f89659bb09680c9f86ee","tid":1550651,"uid":41262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:35.000Z","msg":"弱智真係有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c998caf902c1a30fcb4a67db815927a793e2ab","tid":1550651,"uid":41262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:14.000Z","msg":"推到佢提早退休"},{"pid":"1ad4f80b990b87ef8aee0fcd3e1cc4dc4c1c634b","tid":1550651,"uid":205844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"打政府工都話情有可原<br />\n呢啲濕鳩廢老睇得多tvb大公報正義上身?"},{"pid":"e83b5b818737c5cb5e82c9c66ec9353e95f47710","tid":1550651,"uid":41262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:03:17.000Z","msg":"以為著緊制服 cosplay緊公安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc38cc9326c3266d88f1bf9638404cf91634009","tid":1550651,"uid":299632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:06.000Z","msg":"無用都照推"},{"pid":"a9af14887e03cd599c0738ef0f54a85f66810390","tid":1550651,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ad4f80b990b87ef8aee0fcd3e1cc4dc4c1c634b","tid":1550651,"uid":205844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"打政府工都話情有可原<br />\n呢啲濕鳩廢老睇得多tvb大公報正義上身?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:49.000Z","msg":"因為佢要報料俾藍絲勇武派做野"},{"pid":"17c4b1d9ac9b0ad465d21f23956af9a676cb84c0","tid":1550651,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b5cbbcc3d9bbba44920d99d599eea9aa9ab685","tid":1550651,"uid":319681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賊眉賊眼"},{"pid":"be956fe19b96590065cd26bfd65b8eb1e2167efa","tid":1550651,"uid":155126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769a61c5e1e51b7c856e02a485f0c476bab7379e","tid":1550651,"uid":41262,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YiCGrDn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-